gov.nih.nlm.ling.core

Interface ContiguousSurfaceElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<SurfaceElement>, Node, SurfaceElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiWord, Word

    public interface ContiguousSurfaceElement
extends SurfaceElement
    An interface for contiguous textual units, which extends SurfaceElement interface. The classes that implement this interface represent textual units without gaps.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
    See Also:
    SurfaceElement, Word, MultiWord
